ke":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"[突發]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gpobserver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgpobserver&d=S6cB4ciL2boPXDS%2BKOaE2QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f46573d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gpobserver</a><br />\n<br />\n天文宅原來總共遞交左6個命名申請，而其餘四個申請依家得到確認，將會以kalafina嘅成員命名<br />\n<br />\n值得留意嘅係命名申請包括埋早已退團嘅maya，由此可見天文宅果然係k團真粉，入坑資歷應該老過其他聽fate或者小圓入坑嘅fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nkalafina宇宙第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca830a358f87cd2c08db99f79d567f7b9e07d4ad","tid":452870,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[突發]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gpobserver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgpobserver&d=S6cB4ciL2boPXDS%2BKOaE2QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f46573d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gpobserver</a><br />\n<br />\n天文宅原來總共遞交左6個命名申請，而其餘四個申請依家得到確認，將會以kalafina嘅成員命名<br />\n<br />\n值得留意嘅係命名申請包括埋早已退團嘅maya，由此可見天文宅果然係k團真粉，入坑資歷應該老過其他聽fate或者小圓入坑嘅fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nkalafina宇宙第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天文宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線"},{"pid":"2a46d584f8a0fd7aed4e24ae257302a0f7c117cc","tid":452870,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"空境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141941bfb67bbae2900f4832bc78c826324fdea5","tid":452870,"uid":91083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DN9mdNHVAAAY21V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDN9mdNHVAAAY21V.jpg&h=fc689a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有日本網友向天文宅查詢並且得到回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同預期一樣天文宅係因為睇左空境而入坑，不過佢係2015年先睇空境同識kalafina，佢仲將梶浦大媽比作現代莫札特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲提及為小行星命名提議嘅其中一個難處係搵相關人士嘅生日(不過呢樣對kalafina應該唔難，年年生日佢地都會更blog)，又話小行星命名過程需要保密所以佢係公佈之前唔可以透露任何野，似乎暗示佢仲有其他acg相關小行星命名提議未公佈"}]}